description.narrative: The development objectives of the proposed project are to: (i) help support Park and County Public Institutions to implement Natura2000 objectives in investment programs; (ii) strengthen capacity for EU-compliant reporting and biodiversity monitoring; and (iii) introduce programs that involve a wide group of stakeholders in Natura 2000 network management.

Finance Agreement :LA. Sch. 2 Sec I.A.3 | Description :Borrower shall maintain, during and until the completion of the Project,thePCC chaired by the State Secretary for Nature Protection of MOC and formed as in MOC Decision no. 612-07/09-44/3 Nov09 |Frequency :Yearly
Finance Agreement :LA. Sch. 2 Sec I.A.4 | Description :The Borrower, through MOC, shall maintain, until the completion of theProject PIU, located within the DSPNCEI under the NPD | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :LA. Sch. 2 Sec I.A.5 | Description :The Borrower, through MOC, shall maintain, until completion of the Project,aProject Support Unit (PSU) within the State Institutefor Nature Protection (SINP) | Frequency :Yearly
